<br>
The hardest part about being a mage.. is we lack escape means.  if you are soloing.. and things go bad.. you are probably going to die if you don't get creative and learn how to control your pet good.  We don't have any way to run faster than the mob (until 51+ or through other items like jboots/sow potions) you can't root (your earth pets can.. but I personally never have used earth pets regularly) you can't hinder mobs movement in any way.. you can't root.. you can't mez.. you can't charm.. (well.. not till 60+.. then you can mez and charm summoned things) In groups.. you have to be aware of your pet (not so much anymore since the aggro changes on pets.. but if they are chasing a running mob they will still aggro assisting mobs) and you have to be sure not to overnuke to the point that the mob wants to eat you.  <br>
